quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  70,40,"Nditsuba khu Nyasaye, Omulesi webukwe nende mumbo, toto efwe khuli nobunyali."
  70,41,"Bwokhukalukhasia abalayi bashilakhwo abo, nafu shikhwakhashilwa tawe."
  70,42,"Kho baleshe mubukalakala nende emibayo chiabu, okhula lwabalinyoolana nende inyanga yabalakwa."
  70,43,"Inyanga yabakharule mubilindwa tsimbiro opara mbu belukhanga okhutsia khumasanamu."
  70,44,"Obweni bwabu bulihenga hasi, tsisoni tsilibafumbeela. Eyo niyo inyanga yabalakungwa."
  71,1,"Toto efwe khwaruma Nuhu khubandu bebe mbu: “Wikanyilisilie abandubo, eshinyasio eshilulu nishishili okhuboolela.”"
  71,2,"Naboola mbu: “Enywe Abandu baanje, toto esie endi Omwikanyilisi wenyu wahabulafu."
  71,3,"Mbu mumulaame Nyasaye, ne mumurie, ne muwulile esie."
  71,4,"Alabaleshela tsimbi tsienyu, ne alabameta tsinyanga okhula indukho yenyu. Toto indukho ya Nyasaye niyuula, yibetsanga yulile. Abaane nimwakhamanyilekhwo!”"
  71,5,"Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, esie enaanjile Abandu banje eshilo nende eshitere."
  71,6,"Habula omulaango kwanje shikwabametela shiosishiosi tawe halali okhwilukha."
  71,7,"Ne toto buli olwa ndabalanganga mbu khonyoole okhubaleshela, bara tsinzala tsiabu mumarwi kabu, nibefunikha muno tsingubo tsiabu, nibekhulumamia, nibooma emirwe obutinyu muno."
  71,8,"Mana khandi toto nebalanga mubwang’aang’u."
  71,9,"Mana khandi nebakhuumila obutinyu, mana khandi nebalaanga mubwifisi muno."
  71,10,"Ne nebaboolela mbu: 'Sabe Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi eshileshelo, toto Ye ni Omunji wokhuleshela."